Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:06.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:09.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:44.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你和它有关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是在问你和「夜祸」有没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道的话就不要惹上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:03.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就应该知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,它不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是夜晚的祸害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:29.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:38.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,繭子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:46.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,吵得这么厉害 无论是谁都会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:48.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:49.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是个小孩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还是叫一下救护车什么的比较好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:04.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,它是晚上的祸害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:57.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这云
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫什么云
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:02.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 积雨云
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天的云
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像天空中有着山一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,它甚至被叫做云峰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一般的绵云
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你救了我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说不上是救…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不还礼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:31.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还想要我做些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,想要你做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能做到的话 什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:57.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:06.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,H…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我给你做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我什么也没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又得重来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.64,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫 森宫依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.42,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 请假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.01,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫经常请假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,从昨天开始就总让人觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.96,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都已经是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很让人担心呢  真名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.63,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,自己要好好注意身体哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个只懂得天空的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有句话「傻瓜不会感冒」的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:56.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又是和天空有关的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 总觉得有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不接 没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为有更担心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再有一会儿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 把这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:28.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有点小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好 三分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:40.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要突然过来阻止嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚不是要踢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是自动贩卖机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,机器的话 用踢就什么毛病都可以修好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:30.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只是微波炉得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但原本是要致谢的… 饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,致谢的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为已经给摸过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 来聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:47.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:48.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 突然之间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你看起来没有朋友 挺寂寞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就重新来自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫依人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,15岁 高一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要光让我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被你看到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我想保密也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:44.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 不是人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫小姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好吃药的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能进行正确的检查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:37.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那边病人正在叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:51.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 有点多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:20.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:22.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是姐姐才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 小依总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:39.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:52.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在经济产业省主办的ECO-Bag竞赛中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:52.27,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,[ECO-Bag]:Ecology bag（无环境污染提袋）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:56.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,入选作品也是使用的由该项技术得以再生的再生布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜祸人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不老不死的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很早以前就总是被追杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天黑后我就会出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:22.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不能见阳光的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:31.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:33.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,活了好几百年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:39.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一次都没有在真正的蓝天下站立过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那光亮 那穿透广阔无边的空间的蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:56.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你说在拍蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 连累你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是晚间新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:15.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还是安全的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为无论怎么受伤 也不会轻易死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:35.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:36.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:57.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:01.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 待在这里比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这里的话 不用担心被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会和谁说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,父母也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说了没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:13.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了吗 这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和那没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为和我在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你总有一天会变得憎恨我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是真名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,马上过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃说要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说是因为依人不来所以就要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:07.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就回来 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一会半会的没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:13.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:33.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:54.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 繭子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:31.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的名菜应该是海鲜才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是我决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:47.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还是好好地跟我说一下发生了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了好几次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜祸没在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:56.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:11.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也没来医院 又没接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,并不想要那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,电灯关着的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:35.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,干吗随便就进来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,本并不打算进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:50.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个… 好狡猾啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:54.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空就是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 比这更美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,更加更加得宽广 美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会给你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:45.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:33.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,sola小知识
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:33.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:35.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,豆科1年 2年生植物中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有豌豆 蚕豆也称天豆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:40.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,它们原产于西南亚洲或北非
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:44.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,据说传到日本是在8世纪
